    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>VODAFONE BOARD MEMBER RESIGNS</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Andrew Ross Sorkin</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Sorkin, Andrew Ross</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Klaus Esser, former chairman of Mannesmann AG, resigns from board of Vodafone Group; Esser joined board on interim basis after Mannesmann acquired Vodafone (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Klaus Esser, the former chairman of Mannesmann A.G., resigned from the board of the Vodafone Group, the world's largest mobile telephone operator. Mr. Esser had joined the board on an interim basis after Mannesmann was acquired by Vodafone for $183 billion in the largest takeover ever. Mr. Esser was paid $27 million in severance pay.</p>
        <p>Andrew Ross Sorkin</p>
      </block>
